title: LFT (for OOL, flex, tournies, etc) - Mid Main - D5
body: I'm diamond 5 currently in soloq and platinum 1 in flex queue and looking for a team. I main mid and I was in the top 13 challenger ranked 5's team in season 6. Add me or comment if you want to recruit me. (Preferred experienced players that are looking to win and a well managed team)
